com.cornell.opencomm.jingleimpl
Class CandidateElementType

java.lang.Object
  com.cornell.opencomm.jingleimpl.BaseElementType
      com.cornell.opencomm.jingleimpl.CandidateElementType

public class CandidateElementType
extends BaseElementType

This Class encapsulates a Candidate Element as described in XEP-0166 (Jingle), XEP-0176 (ICE UDP) and XEP-0177 (Jingle RAW UDP) The class also declares attributes and elements that would be needed during ICE Negotiations. Please refer to the schemas in the respective specifications to understand the structure.

Author:
Abhishek, Ming
